Enter the number: 456a
Is the number hexa-decimal: false

Enter the number: 43A56F
Is the number hexa-decimal: true


CODE--
package myfirst;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class MyFirst {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.print("Enter the number: ");
        String n = sc.nextLine();
        System.out.println("Is the number hexa-decimal: "+n.matches("[0-9A-F]+"));
    }    
}
